        <h2>What the Research Found About the Depo Shot</h2>
        <p class="lead">For decades, women got the Depo-Provera birth control shot without knowing it could cause brain tumors. New research has changed everything.</p>
        <div class="awareness_points">
          <div class="awareness_point">
            <div class="awareness_point_icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Science Proves the Risk</strong>
              <p>A major medical study found that women who used Depo-Provera were <strong>5 times more likely</strong> to develop a brain tumor called a meningioma — especially if they used it for more than one year.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="awareness_point">
            <div class="awareness_point_icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Women Were Never Warned</strong>
              <p>For nearly 30 years, women who used Depo-Provera were never told about the risk of brain tumors. Women who used it before 2019 had no idea this risk existed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="awareness_point">
            <div class="awareness_point_icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Pfizer Is Being Held Responsible</strong>
              <p>Pfizer, the company that makes Depo-Provera, is facing lawsuits across the country. Courts have brought these cases together in a federal program called an MDL — making it easier for women to fight back.</p>
